表的代码预览业务-转运表

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_transfer')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_transfer
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_transfer */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_transfer (
tranID int not null,
trancode nvarchar(20) null,
count int null,
status int null,
expressID int null,
expresscode nvarchar(20) null,
apptime datetime null,
constraint PK_BUSI_TRANSFER primary key (tranID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_transfer') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname

'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_transfer'

end
